The port is great, and the widescreen support is wonderful. However, it has some awful social network called "Gree" integrated. So it tries to get you to make an account there. And here's the worse bit - the Gree icon (a big blue hexagon or octagon) is always in the upper left corner of the screen. Not only is it ugly and distracting, it covers up the score and part of the play area.  SNK are idiots for integrating that garbage in an otherwise fantastic game. How about porting it to PC and putting it on Steam? No, not your own crappy digital storefront. Steam or GoG.
